{"tid":2345574,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件有心 / 唔小心做過最仆街既事","createTime":"2020-12-29T15:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T08:31:20.000Z","uid":75100,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fa0f52d26f46a40da5a8c5397c549dadc35ebb34","tid":2345574,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:08:45.000Z","msg":"我係中三個年有日心情勁差，唔知點解攞左包朱古力奶入廁所望住窗出面飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個窗出面就係牆，望落去會見到少少人地個廁所的<br />\n而個一刻我越諗越嬲，然後一時控制唔住成包野扔左出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啪一聲打左落牆度，然後撞左下水管...再撞多下水管....然後居然入撚左人地廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好死唔死，仲要咁岩條友柯緊屎，我就係上層望住包野滑入去，一野撻落去擠到佢成地奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一秒條友即刻勁大聲:「屌你老母柯緊屎 邊條打靶仔dum包奶落黎，仆你個街再有下次我報警呀!!」，我淆到即刻縮返個頭入去，然後勁大聲係咁講「對唔住比次機會」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n概念圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g40xHpF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg40xHpF.png&h=c407d4cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0a9b334a4248ac482661c86ae6b530d5916ab21","tid":2345574,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:10:50.000Z","msg":"Gay post"},{"pid":"b838f5d72e0910e8505331e4a294aa18b4d0cfa1","tid":2345574,"uid":24457,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:15:53.000Z","msg":"正皮係比幅圖嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686260aeb40b0e90bee62e8c405b1a46a87ea83a","tid":2345574,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1811a9e0118b08551f1cd0f558bee7b236a66f79","tid":2345574,"uid":34333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"原來條友係你..."},{"pid":"9445ce44e3afb7633d9d6ca75e4d913fa4e38699","tid":2345574,"uid":118945,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:52:39.000Z","msg":"好耐之前夜晚同個朋友去公園操gym<br />\n有一班5、6歲小朋友踩單車，父母睇住佢哋玩<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朋友：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：啲細路好嘈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：無啊，有人咩？啊，有啊，有幾個大人囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你睇真啲？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：無啊，你係咪眼花啊，繼續操體能啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：單車窩！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：有幾隻鐵馬囉，無單車<br />\n如是者，佢不停問，不停望，我都堅持話無<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><span class=\"large\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><span class=\"large\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><span class=\"x-large\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n其實我見到，但扮到好堅定好似見唔到<br />\n之後我同佢走經過嘅之後依然扮見唔到<br />\n佢好似真係嚇親，之後等佢驚完一輪，我先同佢講其實我整蠱佢。"},{"pid":"c84895c8b9d6aa61631d7aefea47237aab99e4de","tid":2345574,"uid":63843,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"小學上上下堂去廁所<br />\n去完聽到廁格有聲問 有冇人係度啊<br />\n我當聽唔到 洗完手 頭也不回走左去<br />\n事後稔返起條友有可能爆石冇廁紙想搵幫拖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係如果我知佢冇廁紙我應該更加唔會理佢 加速走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdc207035a7902b19b1c21f7427b171b5f3eee0","tid":2345574,"uid":379538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa0f52d26f46a40da5a8c5397c549dadc35ebb34","tid":2345574,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:08:45.000Z","msg":"我係中三個年有日心情勁差，唔知點解攞左包朱古力奶入廁所望住窗出面飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個窗出面就係牆，望落去會見到少少人地個廁所的<br />\n而個一刻我越諗越嬲，然後一時控制唔住成包野扔左出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啪一聲打左落牆度，然後撞左下水管...再撞多下水管....然後居然入撚左人地廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好死唔死，仲要咁岩條友柯緊屎，我就係上層望住包野滑入去，一野撻落去擠到佢成地奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一秒條友即刻勁大聲:「屌你老母柯緊屎 邊條打靶仔dum包奶落黎，仆你個街再有下次我報警呀!!」，我淆到即刻縮返個頭入去，然後勁大聲係咁講「對唔住比次機會」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n概念圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g40xHpF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg40xHpF.png&h=c407d4cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:02:38.000Z","msg":"舊屎畫得幾靚"},{"pid":"0401f86ff9079165748d00915b19c4ac348422f5","tid":2345574,"uid":118945,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:04:43.000Z","msg":"講個構思嘅故事俾大家聽：<br />\n<br />\n從前海港城好撚多大劣人同啲打卡點/維港自拍<br />\n嗰陣返份新工，啱啱畢業壓力好大<br />\n<br />\n咁就企喺尖沙嘴碼頭發呆<br />\n望住被大劣人侵佔嘅海港，諗起下午俾老細屌柒完，一時怒上心頭<br />\n<br />\ndownload咗一啲令人為之側目嘅豬閪照片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後airdrop俾哂啲個名係簡體字嘅iPhone人<br />\n<br />\n一路挨住欄杆，觀賞airdrop豬閪俾人嘅眾生相<br />\n<br />\n有啲大劣妹：幹，巧恐怖<br />\n有啲自拍嘅肥毒大劣人連iPhone都差啲跌撚埋落維港<br />\n<br />\n突然，壓力就紓解了。"},{"pid":"ae66a60b44842676aa40660b541277946312440c","tid":2345574,"uid":79865,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba8346067f85112c4ca8779f0fbf74889c2c894","tid":2345574,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T20:20:39.000Z","msg":"有個fd用ig識女嗰啲平台課咗金買咗格story,我見到之後即刻9秒9cut圖po上我個story tag埋佢問佢點解條友咁似你<br />\n個story話佢有米7,其實佢真人無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09dcae70e564058243b225aab33bb1fd7341790","tid":2345574,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T22:04:25.000Z","msg":"幾好笑"},{"pid":"7fb9e9a166fb4db60077e0a463dee0d8071211ac","tid":2345574,"uid":305799,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T22:06:41.000Z","msg":"食咗女朋友個閨蜜搞到佢哋不和<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b064805a94819ed09af80081f00b76944e90a525","tid":2345574,"uid":157727,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T22:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afddcf2892a2facec5625db8e3cf82127f848a80","tid":2345574,"uid":168156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:29:13.000Z","msg":"中學要買咩愛心券，幫個同學寫左買10張<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbc1bde18b885c78d051b6c24227fc0e7e6c943","tid":2345574,"uid":281492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7fb9e9a166fb4db60077e0a463dee0d8071211ac","tid":2345574,"uid":305799,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T22:06:41.000Z","msg":"食咗女朋友個閨蜜搞到佢哋不和<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"閨你老母蜜咩"},{"pid":"b92489596ac8ed66edda72e9c6b50f398dccc0c2","tid":2345574,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afddcf2892a2facec5625db8e3cf8212